# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# IMPORTANT: data/, mlruns/, src/, chromadb/ are NOT ignored.
# The backend container requires:
#   data/03_processed/master_smartphones.parquet  → /predict and /api/v1/market-data
#   data/chromadb/                                → ChromaDB vector store for /chat
#   mlruns/                                       → MLflow unified Pipeline artifact
#   src/                                          → All application source code
